{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"One way to change our genes is to make new ones,"},{"time":2000,"text":"as Craig Venter has so elegantly shown."},{"time":4000,"text":"Another is to change our lifestyles."},{"time":7000,"text":"And what we're learning is how powerful and dynamic these changes can be,"},{"time":11000,"text":"that you don't have to wait very long to see the benefits."},{"time":14000,"text":"When you eat healthier, manage stress, exercise and love more,"},{"time":19000,"text":"your brain actually gets more blood flow and more oxygen."},{"time":21000,"text":"But more than that, your brain gets measurably bigger."},{"time":24000,"text":"Things that were thought impossible just a few years ago"},{"time":26000,"text":"can actually be measured now."},{"time":28000,"text":"This was figured out by Robin Williams"},{"time":31000,"text":"a few years before the rest of us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"Now, there's some things that you can do"},{"time":35000,"text":"to make your brain grow new brain cells."},{"time":38000,"text":"Some of my favorite things, like chocolate and tea, blueberries,"},{"time":40000,"text":"alcohol in moderation, stress management"},{"time":44000,"text":"and cannabinoids found in marijuana."},{"time":46000,"text":"I'm just the messenger."},{"time":49000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":52000,"text":"What were we just talking about?"},{"time":55000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":57000,"text":"And other things that can make it worse,"},{"time":59000,"text":"that can cause you to lose brain cells."},{"time":61000,"text":"The usual suspects, like saturated fat and sugar,"},{"time":64000,"text":"nicotine, opiates, cocaine, too much alcohol and chronic stress."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68000,"text":"Your skin gets more blood flow when you change your lifestyle,"},{"time":71000,"text":"so you age less quickly. Your skin doesn't wrinkle as much."},{"time":74000,"text":"Your heart gets more blood flow."},{"time":76000,"text":"We've shown that you can actually reverse heart disease."},{"time":78000,"text":"That these clogged arteries that you see on the upper left,"},{"time":81000,"text":"after only a year become measurably less clogged."},{"time":83000,"text":"And the cardiac PET scan shown on the lower left,"},{"time":85000,"text":"the blue means no blood flow."},{"time":87000,"text":"A year later -- orange and white is maximum blood flow."},{"time":90000,"text":"We've shown you may be able to stop and reverse the progression"},{"time":93000,"text":"of early prostate cancer and, by extension, breast cancer,"},{"time":95000,"text":"simply by making these changes."},{"time":97000,"text":"We've found that tumor growth in vitro was inhibited"},{"time":100000,"text":"70 percent in the group that made these changes,"},{"time":102000,"text":"whereas only nine percent in the comparison group."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105000,"text":"These differences were highly significant."},{"time":107000,"text":"Even your sexual organs get more blood flow,"},{"time":109000,"text":"so you increase sexual potency."},{"time":111000,"text":"One of the most effective anti-smoking ads was done"},{"time":113000,"text":"by the Department of Health Services,"},{"time":115000,"text":"showing that nicotine, which constricts your arteries,"},{"time":117000,"text":"can cause a heart attack or a stroke,"},{"time":119000,"text":"but it also causes impotence."},{"time":121000,"text":"Half of guys who smoke are impotent."},{"time":123000,"text":"How sexy is that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":124000,"text":"Now we're also about to publish a study --"},{"time":126000,"text":"the first study showing you can change gene expression in men with prostate cancer."},{"time":129000,"text":"This is what's called a heat map --"},{"time":131000,"text":"and the different colors -- and along the side, on the right, are different genes."},{"time":134000,"text":"And we found that over 500 genes were favorably changed --"},{"time":137000,"text":"in effect, turning on the good genes, the disease-preventing genes,"},{"time":140000,"text":"turning off the disease-promoting genes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144000,"text":"And so these findings I think are really very powerful,"},{"time":147000,"text":"giving many people new hope and new choices."},{"time":149000,"text":"And companies like Navigenics and DNA Direct and 23andMe,"},{"time":154000,"text":"that are giving you your genetic profiles,"},{"time":157000,"text":"are giving some people a sense of, \"Gosh, well, what can I do about it?\""},{"time":160000,"text":"Well, our genes are not our fate, and if we make these changes --"},{"time":163000,"text":"they're a predisposition -- but if we make bigger changes"},{"time":165000,"text":"than we might have made otherwise,"},{"time":167000,"text":"we can actually change how our genes are expressed."},{"time":170000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":171000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}